                        <head>
                            <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                        </head>
                        <p>At the end of October a paper entitled “United States Policy With Respect
                            to Berlin and Eastern Germany” was submitted to the National Security
                            Council, becoming <gloss target="#t_NSC1">NSC</gloss> 89 on October 20.
                            Regarding this paper, see the Paper prepared by McCloy and others,
                            August 29, <ref target="#pg_867">page 867</ref>.</p>
